  "folder": "fhSubModern00001",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>An aerosolized blend of three commercial stimulants and a fourth ingredient the lab denies, sold in dented inhalers from gas-station back rooms. Three sharp puffs are tradition; two will do; four ends a career.</p><p><strong><em>Desired effects on use.</em></strong> For 1 hour you have advantage on initiative rolls and on Dexterity (Acrobatics) checks.</p><p><strong><em>On use, save against addiction.</em></strong> Make a DC 13 Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, you gain the Addicted condition from Triple-Burn (see below).</p><p><strong><em>Addicted from Triple-Burn.</em></strong> While you have this Addicted condition, you are also Poisoned and have disadvantage on Charisma checks (you talk too fast and finish other people's sentences badly).</p><p><strong><em>Withdrawal Modifier: 3.</em></strong> Withdrawal lasts max(3 &minus; your Constitution modifier, 2) long rests, minimum 1.</p><p><em>Requires: Inhaler.</em></p>"
    },
